extendedInfo.description: Pregnant? Need a pregnancy kick and/or movement counter?Keep track of your baby's kicks and movements with a 60 minute countdown timer.  The countdown timer will continue to count down until 60 minutes is over or until you exit the app.  You may hit the HOME key to temporarily leave your counting session.  The countdown will continue to go unless you leave the app for a long period of time.Tap the top button (movement) to count a movement of your baby, or tap the bottom button (kick) to count a kick.When you're done, record your movements/kicks if desired.upcoming feature: saving a history of all count sessions, emailing/sharing your count session results-to save your count session, hit the back button and appropriate action from dialog

reviews.comment: Logs time when kicks stop not when they start. So if baby is very active at 12pm for 30mins its logged at 12.30 so not accurate. Good kick counter tho
